        Constructs a KeyStoreDetails object.
        Parameters:
        type - the KeyStoreType.
        provider - the keystore Provider string identifier.
        filename - the filename for where the keystore is located. "NONE" if the keystore type is PKCS11.
        password - the password to access the keystore.
